skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my gym angel
des: Start every morning by saying, "Alexa, open My Gym Angel." Gathered from Pinterest and Instagram, these motivational quotes will give you the extra push you need to get up and get moving on days when you really need it. Geared towards body builders, power lifters and cross fitters, these quotations target those who are serious about health and fitness, but who sometimes need a little extra motivation for those 5:30am workouts.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
